Wat ga je doen?

PostNL is becoming a postal tech company. As Senior C# Engineer you are part of a multi-disciplinary Business-IT-team comprising among others, a Lead Engineer, Developers and Solution Consultants. As a fully collaborative team, together you are responsible for the development of components within our logistic software environment. Within your team, new software applications are primarily built in C# making use of various AWS functionalities for optimal scalability.

Responsibilities include:
Translating our complex logistic business processes and requirements regarding, for example; order management, planning, distribution and transport, into functional applications using reliable C# code;
